{"tid":1607731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師 : 未成年被捕人記住6點","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:43:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce925fca852cc6adcd78dd667c94301b042df13","tid":1607731,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191001/60102710\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60102710&h=9a23e87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/oTqHkKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTqHkKV.png&h=808c43d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n律師陳惠源提醒未成年被捕人注意事項。(資料圖片)<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1001 00:05<br />\n<br />\n家長若提司法覆核，勝算有多高？若失敗是否須付過百萬律師費？律師陳惠源認為，司法覆核裁判官判入兒童院的裁定，法官主要看父母的監管能力，例如會否經常不在香港，如渉案兒童在社署有離家出走紀錄，勝算會大大降低。陳又指，過百萬律師費不是沒可能，但只是考慮到最差情況。「律政司搵到最高級律師同你打官司，咁係假設政府用盡方法要將未成年人送入兒童院。」"},{"pid":"15af918ca6ae4747f01215f657bd759ea6859780","tid":1607731,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191001/60102710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60102710&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=4c55c732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60102710&h=da3e1bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191001/60102710</a>"},{"pid":"5d290c57b6768b3f0213c33ced62e097a081b299","tid":1607731,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"祝大家今日武運昌隆 平安歸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face